.TH "fl6_update_dst" 9 "fl6_update_dst" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
fl6_update_dst \- update flowi destination address with info given by srcrt option, if any.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "struct in6_addr *" fl6_update_dst
.BI "(struct flowi6 *fl6 "  ","
.BI "const struct ipv6_txoptions *opt "  ","
.BI "struct in6_addr *orig "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "fl6" 12
flowi6 for which daddr is to be updated
.IP "opt" 12
struct ipv6_txoptions in which to look for srcrt opt
.IP "orig" 12
copy of original daddr address if modified
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Returns NULL if no txoptions or no srcrt, otherwise returns orig
and initial value of fl6->daddr set in orig
